strategy = backtestStrategy( ___ ,Name,Value) sets properties on page 15-242 using name-
value pair arguments and any of the arguments in the previous syntax. You can specify multiple
name-value pair arguments. For example, strat =
backtestStrategy('MyStrategy',@myRebalFcn,'TransactionCost',0.005,'LookbackWi
ndow',20).
